text: Gisele Cristina Florentino (born 1 August 1973) is a Brazilian female volleyball player. She played for the Brazil women's national volleyball team at the 1999 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Cup, and 2001 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Grand Champions Cup. == References == == External links == * * * Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian women's volleyball players
